@prefix sub: <https://w3id.org/np/RApRo_jZo4zy-Xz84vbejke7hbBm7_P-pvsm2d7ATX7NE/> .
@prefix biochementity: <https://w3id.org/peh/biochementities/> .
@prefix dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix np: <http://www.nanopub.org/nschema#> .
